  "body": "Hope to provide `render(props, state)` !\r\n\r\n````js\r\nclass App extends Component {\r\n\r\n    constructor(props) {\r\n        super(props);\r\n\r\n        this.state = {\r\n            active: 0,\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    render({ name, age }, { active }) {\r\n        return (\r\n            <div>\r\n                props: name = {name}\r\n                props: age = {age}\r\n                state: active = {active}\r\n            </div>\r\n        );\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/// ---- use\r\n<App name='jon' age={20} />\r\n````\r\n",
